==== TSPO-PET Imaging

    - #super[11]C-PBR28 or #super[18]F-DPA-714 radioligand (TSPO-specific tracers)
    - Standardized uptake value (SUV) analysis in predefined regions of interest (basal ganglia, thalamus, brainstem, prefrontal cortex)
    - Distribution volume ratio (DVR) to derive binding potential
    - Whole-brain voxel-wise analyses to identify activation hotspots

